Comment: I play the usual King's pawn opening.
A normal game.
I attack the pawn with my knight.
He attacks my pawn with his knight.
I bring my other knight out.
We have a four knights opening.
I bring my bishop out attacking the knight.
He comes in and attacks my knight. Not the usual move.
I castle.
He takes my knight.
I take back with my queen.
He moves his bishop out, probably to make room to castle.
I move my pawn up.
He castles.
I bring my bishop out attacking his other knight.
He moves his pawn, attacking my bishop.
I move my bishop back.
He moves another pawn up attacking my bishop.
I move my bishop back.
He moves another pawn up thats about to attack me.
